<typeStatus box="[915,1018,1926,1952]" pageId="1" pageNumber="34">holotype</typeStatus>
comes from Chinkultic (an archeological site of the Mayan culture in the Parque Nacional Lagunas de Montebello, La Trinitaria Municipality in Chiapas; 
